n<br />\n政府發言人表示，目前疫情仍然嚴峻，防控疫情仍然是政府目前的首要工作，但考慮到社會運作的需要，各政策局及部門須採取針對性措施減少社交接觸，以及在實施預防感染措施的前提下，由8月24日起逐步恢復提供更多基本公共服務。政府的最終目標是在條件許可下全面恢復正常公共服務。各政策局和部門若需要時間部署人手、物資和作出所需調整，或會分階段恢復服務。有關部門會就其最新服務安排的詳情另行作出公布。(ek/da)"},{"pid":"15e9a9f1af6f32db5613f852ae3c0f4f39babc03","tid":2166230,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e72492fb1c06e257ca580d02211383fb5e2754","tid":2166230,"uid":60892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"WFH期間聽到最多係 我WFH喎，有咩事留返返公司先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f67fb60d57a6284a1cbf92a454f85add3fe517b","tid":2166230,"uid":169568,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"抵你班仆街死啦 無社會生產力既垃圾 一日到黑都掛住wfh"},{"pid":"7a55f250d636abff4da0e8ba1a87836ad209510d","tid":2166230,"uid":84054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:36:45.000Z","msg":"無得打fall guys<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb0d63f493151e6e01d3372506853c6a771165","tid":2166230,"uid":94007,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6f67fb60d57a6284a1cbf92a454f85add3fe517b","tid":2166230,"uid":169568,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"抵你班仆街死啦 無社會生產力既垃圾 一日到黑都掛住wfh"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"之前某個公墓員Post 仲話最好WFH 三年<br />\n咁撚唔鍾意返工<br />\n辭鳩左佢咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56139619ea8b5b331b5398d72a35c4322d0ee545","tid":2166230,"uid":169568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f67fb60d57a6284a1cbf92a454f85add3fe517b","tid":216